TEAM!
Hey friends!
Just a quick update so y'all know I'm still alive and making this; work on MFG is still ongoing, and is entirely in the "Art and Layout" phase. The layout is looking slick, and the art is coming along great, Andi's already finished some big pieces, and they think there's a good chance the rest will be done by the end of the month. Assuming things stick to that, I expect we should have the PDF finished pretty soon, fingers crossed. In the meantime I was thinking of publishing a simple, format/artless copy of the rules so y'all can just get into it. We'll chat more about that at SPG HQ. Till then, here's some cool pics;
